title: TypeError when creating a tensorflow.keras model with TCN layer - keras-tcn
body:
Hi all,
I have recently started to study temporal convolutional networks and I was trying to implement a model using the keras-tcn library.
To get familiar with the library, I tried to run the example script for regression task presented in the README file, but I get the following error when the Sequential model is created:
